TI  - Ultrasonographic Detection of Micro-Bubbles in the Right Atrium to Confirm Peripheral Venous Catheter Position in Children.
AU  - Takeshita, Jun MD, PhD
AU  - Nakajima, Yasufumi MD, PhD
AU  - Kawamura, Atsushi MD
